thread.title: Health Fair underway

title: Health Fair underway
text: By Union Democrat staff October 21, 2015 01:00 am Health Fair attendees browse booths Tuesday at the Mother Lode Fairgrounds. Maggie Beck / Union Democrat, Copyright 2015. The Tuolumne County Health Fair opened Tuesday at the Mother Lode Fairgrounds in Sonora, and continues today. Fair hours are from 7 a.m. to 3 p.m. The annual event offers low-cost health screenings and health-related information. Follow UnionDemocrat.com
